nd thus the activity of telomerase is associated with signal strength. In samples lacking telomerase, oligonucleotides are not able to hybridise with sDNA.

Dungchai et al. [59] merged the concept of electrochemical detection with μ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
