				\begin{document}$$H_2 O_2$$\end{document}, and pH was published by Guinati et al. [195]. To ensure that the paper was completely cut without any surface damage, the EVA-coated polyester Gazela laminator model was used to laminate the paper at 140∘C\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
